description:
"Lay Low and Pretty" is the title of Skypiper's DEBUT album released in May of 2008.  The packaging consists of an "O" sleeve covering a jewel case. The 6-panel insert enclosed displays the lyrics, credits, and a full presentation of the album's artwork.
This album contains 11 songs.

